{"tid":2203713,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"成日出現但你又不能理解/覺得不合理既劇情","createTime":"2020-09-15T13:49:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T16:55:19.000Z","uid":42246,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d959d5c535e35a0d70d074f9dd36a1d5f74b1060","tid":2203713,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T13:49:39.000Z","msg":"以前tvb 好興女主角死左<br />\n大結局會係男主角最後遇到一個同女主角一模一樣既路人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但我由細細個第一次見到依個劇情已經大叫左出來<br />\n就算似樣都唔會係同一個女仔 咁點會叫做happy ending<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 拍來做乜鳩<br />\n<br />\n點知依個劇情係tvb重覆又重覆 都唔知班編劇點去理解件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再大個d發現連美國電影 美劇都有類似劇情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n美劇f檔案 睇到去season 3/4 reboot左一次世界<br />\n我到依家都諗緊個女主角係咪同一個女主角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a56f487ee5eb1368e417a3cbfe988cc9792dd6b","tid":2203713,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T13:50:51.000Z","msg":"樓主講得勁中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74fcfd5537ef59ec9ba10e0ee2678af2980e1884","tid":220371